Wychavon Contest (Championship Section) 1 Entertainments Contest Wychavon Festival of Brass wychavon-contest-championship-section
De Montfort (High) School, Evesham, Worcestershire, England, UK Eccles Borough Band invited to 2017 Spring Festival, Blackpool.
Winning Conductor awarded the Evesham Town Plate: Mareika Gray The WFB Entertainment Trophy (best Presentation): Sandhurst Silver The WFB Soloist Trophy: Tim De Maesenner (Tenor Horn), Medway Band The Centre Stage Percussion Trophy: Verwood Concert Brass Prizes - 1st £1250, 2nd £650, 3rd £325. 16 bands competed.
